{"tid":1833927,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"基斯文成立電競隊招攬好手","createTime":"2020-01-22T06:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T13:56:12.000Z","uid":226925,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f55a79de42c02ee7c776af41f8b7d55dec61d6ae","tid":1833927,"uid":226925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:53:34.000Z","msg":"法國球星基斯文宣佈成立以自己為名的電競隊，並公開尋找高手加盟。<br />\n<br />\n電子競技形成全球熱潮，不少運動明星都成立電競隊，巴塞隆拿球星基斯文（Antoine Griezmann）周二也在社交網站推出廣告，宣佈成立Grizi Esport電競隊，並開始招聘全球高手，將參加Fortnite、CSGO等大型比賽。<br />\n<br />\n目前成立電競隊的球星包括NBA球星奧尼爾、巴西球星尼馬等，但基斯文跟上述球星不同的是，其他人只是投資者，但基斯文將參與管理，其弟Theo將擔任球隊的總經理。<br />\n<br />\n該宣傳片段放上網1天左右，已經有34.5萬人點擊，獲得1.1萬人like，看來將有不少電競高手爭相求職。<br />\n<br />\n相關片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AntoGriezmann/status/1219318567042199553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAntoGriezmann%2Fstatus%2F1219318567042199553&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmFIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=a3c367b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAntoGriezmann%2Fstatus%2F1219318567042199553&h=af512a53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AntoGriezmann/status/1219318567042199553</a>"},{"pid":"da31b69262eb880496dad4702bc7d9b6163e0f26","tid":1833927,"uid":5600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"Logo隻企鵝成隻QQ咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27210634ecadde1e427d61262acb85b749aece65","tid":1833927,"uid":204306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會請埋丹比利打FIFA<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12afb2448e3690545cbd68aa71901a5b56eb4e62","tid":1833927,"uid":226925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27210634ecadde1e427d61262acb85b749aece65","tid":1833927,"uid":204306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0